snippet.title: Olivier Gomis
snippet.description:
Hello welcome to my YouTube channel, I'm a 23 french guy who enjoy making stuff out of wood and sharing it on the interwebs.
Bienvenue sur ma chaîne YouTube, je suis un menuisier et tourneur pro passionné de 23 ans j'espère que vous trouverez votre bonheur ici.

--DISCLAIMER-- This is NOT an educational channel. Everything I do and the machines that I use are the things that I'm confortable doing. That doesn't mean it the best or the only way to do it. DO NOT replicate things you see me doing if you feel unconfortable or unsafe. ALWAYS be aware of the danger and the injuries that can appen when using heavy machinery and power tools. You are the only respondsable for your own safty and for those who might be around you when working.

Please don't contact me about uploading my videos on your facebook page, no matter how much followers you have. I am not interested. 
My videos are copyrighted, please respect that as it is a matter of law.
